	<Notes>This sequel to 1986's Rolling Thunder, you play the role of an agent working your way towards GELDRA headquarters. You are armed only with a handgun with limited ammo, which can be replenished by entering doors or even upgraded if you find the right door. This game adds co-operative mode which its predecessor lacked. Now two players can play simultaneously, with one player being a female agent named Leila and the other player controlling the male agent "Albatross".</Notes>
